    {
      "scene_id": "scene_001",
      "scene_number": 1,
      "text": "INT. OLD VICTORIAN HOUSE - LIVING ROOM - NIGHT\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:00:00]\nRain lashes the windows. EMMA (32, tired single mom) sits on a worn couch, scrolling her phone. Her daughter LILY (8) sleeps upstairs. The house creaks\u2014old pipes, settling wood.\n\nEMMA\n(soft, to herself)\nJust one more bill paid... then bed.\n\nA faint WHISPER from the wall behind her. Indistinct. She freezes.\n\nEMMA\nHello?\n\nSilence. She shakes it off, stands, walks to the kitchen.",
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 90.0,
      "duration": 90.0,
      "emotion": "tension",
      "emotion_confidence": 0.7,
      "secondary_emotions": [
