    {
      "scene_id": "scene_002",
      "scene_number": 2,
      "text": "INT. KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:01:30]\nEmma pours water. The whisper again\u2014closer, like breath on her neck.\n\nWHISPER (O.S.)\n...stay...\n\nEmma spins. Nothing. She laughs nervously.\n\nEMMA\nOld house. Just the wind.\n\nShe heads upstairs.",
