    {
      "scene_id": "scene_003",
      "scene_number": 3,
      "text": "INT. UPSTAIRS HALLWAY - NIGHT\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:03:00]\nEmma checks on Lily. The girl is peaceful, clutching a stuffed bear. Emma kisses her forehead.\n\nEMMA\n(whispering)\nSweet dreams, baby.\n\nAs she turns to leave, the bedroom door creaks shut behind her\u2014slowly, on its own. Emma stops.\n\nEMMA\nLily?\n\nNo answer. She pushes the door open. Lily is gone. Bed empty.\n\nEMMA\n(panicked)\nLily!\n\nShe rushes downstairs.",
      "start": 180.0,
      "end": 300.0,
