    {
      "scene_id": "scene_005",
      "scene_number": 5,
      "text": "INT. BASEMENT STAIRS - NIGHT\n\n[Approx. Timestamp: 00:07:30]\nEmma, flashlight in hand, descends slowly. The whispers lead her down.\n\nWHISPERS\n...down here... she's waiting...\n\nAt the bottom: the basement is empty except for an old mirror covered in dust. Emma approaches.\n\nShe wipes the glass. Her reflection stares back\u2014but it's not moving with her. The reflection smiles.\n\nREFLECTION EMMA\n(soft, eerie)\nYou've been gone so long, Emma. We missed you.\n\nEmma backs away. The mirror cracks\u2014slow spiderweb fractures.\n\nSuddenly, LILY'S VOICE from behind the mirror.\n\nLILY (O.S.)\nMommy... help...\n\nEmma smashes the mirror with her elbow. Glass shatters. Darkness swallows the room.\n\nThe whispers become screams\u2014inhuman.\n\nEMMA\n(screaming)\nGive her back!",
